\c 24
\s Dhavhidhi anokamura vapristi
\p
\v 1 Zvino vanakomana vaAroni vaiva nemapoka avo. Vanakomana vaAroni: Nadhabhi, naAbhihu, Eriazari, naItamari\x + Num.. 26.60.\x*.
\v 2 Asi Nadhabhi naAbhihu vakafa kutangira baba vavo, uye vaiva vasina vana. Naizvozvo Eriazari naItamari vakashanda paupristi\x + Rev. 10.1.\x*.
\v 3 Dhavhidhi ndokuvakamura, naZadhoki pavanakomana vaEriazari, naAhimereki\x + 6.8. 24.31,6. 2 Sam. 8.17. 1 Madz. 2.26,35.\x* pavanakomana vaItamari, zvichienderana nezvinzvimbo zvavo pashumiro yavo\x + 6.8. 24.31,6. 2 Sam. 8.17. 1 Madz. 2.26,35.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino kwakawanikwa kuvanakomana vaEriazari misoro yevane simba vazhinji kupfuura kuvanakomana vaItamari; ndokuvakamura: Pavanakomana vaEriazari, misoro yeimba yemadzibaba yaiva gumi nemitanhatu\x + 24.6,30. Num.. 1.2.\x*, uye pavanakomana vaItamari neimba yemadzibaba avo\x + 24.6,30. Num.. 1.2.\x* vasere.
\v 5 Zvino vakakamurwa nemijenya, ava neavo; nokuti machinda eimba tsvene nemachinda aMwari aibva pavanakomana vaEriazari nepavanakomana vaItamari\x + 24.31. Vato. 20.9.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino Shemaya mwanakomana waNetaneri munyori, anobva kuVaRevhi, wakavanyora pamberi pamambo, nemachinda, naZadhoki mupristi\x + 6.8. 24.31,6. 2 Sam. 8.17. 1 Madz. 2.26,35.\x*, naAhimereki\x + 6.8. 24.31,6. 2 Sam. 8.17. 1 Madz. 2.26,35.\x* mwanakomana waAbhiyatari\x + 18.16. 27.34. 1 Sam. 22.20. 23.6,9. 2 Sam. 15.35. 20.25. 1 Madz. 1.7.\x*, nemisoro yemadzibaba evapristi neeVaRevhi; imba yababa imwe yatorerwa Eriazari, uye imwe yatorerwa Itamari.
\v 7 Zvino mujenya wekutanga wakabudira kuna Jehoiyaribhi; wepiri kuna Jedhaya\x + 9.12. Ezi. 2.36,37,39.\x*;
\v 8 wetatu kuna Harimi; wechina kuna Seorimi\x + 9.12. Ezi. 2.36,37,39.\x*;
\v 9 weshanu kuna Marikiya; wetanhatu kuna Miyamini\x + 9.12.\x*;
\v 10 wechinomwe kuna Hakozi; wesere kuna Abhija\x + Ruk. 1.5.\x*;
\v 11 wepfumbamwe kuna Jeshuwa; wegumi kuna Shekaniya;
\v 12 wegumi neumwe kuna Eriashibhi; wegumi nemiviri kuna Jakimi;
\v 13 wegumi nemitatu kuna Hupa; wegumi nemina kuna Jeshebhiyabhi;
\v 14 wegumi nemishanu kuna Bhiriga; wegumi nemitanhatu kuna Imeri\x + 9.12. Ezi. 2.36,37,39.\x*;
\v 15 wegumi neminomwe kuna Heziri; wegumi nemisere kuna Hapizezi;
\v 16 wegumi nemipfumbamwe kuna Petahiya; wemakumi maviri kuna Jehezekeri;
\v 17 wemakumi maviri neumwe kuna Jakini; wemakumi maviri nemiviri kuna Gamuri;
\v 18 wemakumi maviri nemitatu kuna Dheraya; wemakumi maviri nemina kuna Mahaziya.
\v 19 Zvinzvimbo zveavo pashumiro yavo zvaiva zvekupinda muimba yaJehovha zvichienderana nekugadzwa kwavo neruoko rwaAroni baba vavo, seizvo Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri zvaakaraira\x + 9.25.\x*.
\s Vakuru vevanakomana vaRevhi
\p
\v 20 Zvino pavanakomana vaRevhi vakasara, pavanakomana vaAmiramu: Shubhaeri; pavanakomana vaShubhaeri: Jehidheya\x + 23.13,17.\x*.
\v 21 PaRehabhiya: Pavanakomana vaRehabhiya, musoro Ishishiya\x + 23.13,17.\x*.
\v 22 PaVaIzihari: Sheromoti; pavanakomana vaSheromoti: Jahati.
\v 23 Nevanakomana \add vaHebhuroni\add*\x + 23.19. 26.31.\x*: Jeria \add wekutanga\add*, Amariya wepiri, Jahaziyeri wetatu, Jekameyamu wechina\x + 23.19. 26.31.\x*.
\v 24 Vanakomana vaUziyeri: Mika\x + 23.20.\x*; pavanakomana vaMika: Shamiri\x + 23.20.\x*.
\v 25 Munin'ina waMika: Ishishiya; pavanakomana vaIshishiya: Zekariya.
\v 26 Vanakomana vaMerari: Mahiri naMushi\x + 23.21.\x*; vanakomana vaJahaziya: Bheno.
\v 27 Vanakomana vaMerari: KwaJahaziya: Bheno, naShohamu, naZakuri, naIbhiri.
\v 28 Pana Mahiri: Eriazari; waiva asina vanakomana\x + 23.22.\x*.
\v 29 Pana Kishi: Vanakomana vaKishi: Jerahimeeri\x + 23.21.\x*.
\v 30 Nevanakomana vaMushi\x + 23.23.\x*: Mahiri, naEdheri, naJerimoti\x + 6.47.\x*. Ava vanakomana vaRevhi zvichienderana neimba yemadzibaba avo.
\v 31 Neavawo vakakanda mijenya sehama dzavo\x + 24.5. 25.8. 26.13,14. Neh. 11.1.\x*, vanakomana vaAroni pamberi paDhavhidhi mambo\x + 24.6.\x*, naZadhoki\x + 6.8. 24.31,6. 2 Sam. 8.17. 1 Madz. 2.26,35.\x*, naAhimereki\x + 6.8. 24.31,6. 2 Sam. 8.17. 1 Madz. 2.26,35.\x*, nemisoro yemadzibaba yevapristi neyeVaRevhi, misoro yemadzibaba seyemunin'ina wake.